{"id":"30784995-daae-42d7-88bd-22a93a7a705a","title":"1552/11/21: To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"599684f5-bef7-4769-824f-a4d311c352fe","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, [November 21st, 1552].","standoffProperties":[{"id":"f183e517-bdde-4025-b018-e523f6106238","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":3,"value":"8532f2fa-b614-4eed-9eae-586327f6a15a","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"db8ee650-34c1-463b-bfff-8bc7f9917922","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":["0|name|Rome"]},{"id":"551a309e-8a6a-4f0e-b3ac-ac136d552101","type":"codex/time-reference","start":12,"end":30,"value":"7dc8cd1a-024f-47b9-9ed5-7a1b59694a8f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"27c3ac45-55c2-4562-850e-c4c50ee877e4","type":"style/superscript","start":23,"end":24,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"42d4284c-f8f7-440f-bb34-1e3999ab61b2","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"cce3aefb-aa09-4fba-bf65-dad5974c5cb2","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b0a5ba0c-50ad-4cbb-aad7-4c731d744353","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":["0|name|Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni (b. 1519/09/25 - d. 1599/11/18)"]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"86188ebb-7a7f-4419-abef-e7b891a5f978","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"a73d7f63-b9d7-4022-a11e-5c36519fc490","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":1,"value":"0c663cc2-dd9f-40ce-b17b-734e41b369ef","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"dcd2a0f5-7fa3-44e5-814e-7350367c5832","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":["0|name|Florence"]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"a4b3f4a4-6bf6-49e6-b74f-ada6a5311bbb","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"611bf3e6-9a6c-447f-a9e6-772aa13dd280","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Lionardo,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0In my opinion things that begin badly cannot end well. From thy last letter I learn that all those promises which were made quite voluntarily\u00A0with regard to the damsel have been withdrawn. I tell thee that although I have written on many occasions urging thee not to look for a dowry I do\u00A0not think thou art therefore obliged to submit to the breaking of promises. As contempt is a powerful weapon I counsel thee to have no more to do with it, unless thou seest so many other advantages that thou\u00A0canst afford to overlook smaller details. As far as this is concerned I do not know exactly how the matter stands, and consequently do not know what to say. Commit thyself to God and be confident that all will turn out for the best. I am sure that, by His grace, it must end well.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"8e04fa62-b3eb-4444-8a0f-0a46984cb61f","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":7,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"0b800933-62cb-4c6f-a29c-d7d4a81a39b5","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":7,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"0959b8d7-ae59-4dde-a1d9-26ca0149309f","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":15,"end":16,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":["0|name|Michelangelo Buonarroti (b. 1475/03/06 - d. 1564/02/18)"]},{"id":"ece51666-33a7-4340-bb6d-daf12931b18b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":72,"end":74,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"e59ebe01-fc50-4a2c-b78b-e864f6c31822","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":88,"end":88,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":